WEBVTT

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:31.120
Brother.

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:32.440
I am sorry.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.410
I will kowtow to you.

00:01:36.120 --> 00:01:37.650
Normally, when people die,

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:39.850
they should be buried in peace.

00:01:40.160 --> 00:01:41.000
What a coincidence.

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:42.200
Heaven is helping me.

00:01:42.759 --> 00:01:44.360
We were born in the same year.

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:46.320
Let's die on the same day.

00:01:49.479 --> 00:01:51.440
You are too heavy, buddy.

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:01.040
Come out.

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:01.520
You,

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:02.090
come out.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.560
I am sorry. Come with me.

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:08.410
Let's go.

00:03:19.840 --> 00:03:20.320
Freeze!

00:03:21.440 --> 00:03:21.920
Freeze!

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:23.560
Tong, I'm going to kill you!

00:03:23.560 --> 00:03:24.440
I'll kill you!

00:03:24.720 --> 00:03:25.800
I'll kill you!

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:41.880
Yan.

00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:48.520
Let me go!

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:51.180
What are you doing?

00:03:55.079 --> 00:03:55.920
We are police.

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:57.760
How did you know

00:03:58.160 --> 00:03:59.490
Liu Jiang would be here?

00:04:03.720 --> 00:04:04.640
Want revenge?

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:09.080
How?

00:04:11.440 --> 00:04:13.100
If you're really determined,

00:04:13.440 --> 00:04:14.700
someone will help you.

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:16.880
He killed my daughter.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:19.440
I'll risk my life for revenge.

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:23.410
He said Liu Jiang would come here tonight.

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:43.159
Master.

00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:44.770
Who are you chasing?

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:46.720
There was a strange person

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:48.380
wearing a black hat and a mask,

00:04:48.440 --> 00:04:49.800
peeping from the shadows.

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:51.040
As soon as I looked over,

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:52.370
He just turned and left.

00:05:07.640 --> 00:05:08.840
You suspect it's him?

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:10.080
Killing with a borrowed knife

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:11.760
while observing from the sidelines.

00:05:11.760 --> 00:05:12.560
It's logical.

00:05:14.200 --> 00:05:15.400
What about Liu Jiang?

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:16.680
What are you drawing?

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:17.960
A big villa.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:19.480
Such a big villa!

00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:22.340
Dad has never lived in a big villa before.

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:24.480
Is there a room for Dad inside?

00:05:24.480 --> 00:05:24.920
Yes.

00:05:25.080 --> 00:05:26.200
Is there a room for you?

00:05:26.200 --> 00:05:26.640
Yes.

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:27.720
Is there a room for Mom?

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:28.160
Yes.

00:05:28.280 --> 00:05:30.120
Then who does Dad share a room with?

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:33.200
Dad, Mom, and I all share a room.

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:34.040
Oh.

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:37.360
Dad will definitely work hard to buy you

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.040
a big villa.

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:40.040
Dad.

00:05:40.080 --> 00:05:42.080
A man gave this to me.

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:44.130
He said he's a good friend of yours.

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:45.760
A man gave it to you?

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:48.120
Which uncle gave this to you?

00:05:48.159 --> 00:05:49.080
Don't forget,

00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:51.520
you have a wife

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:52.840
and a child.

00:05:53.320 --> 00:05:54.960
If you want to live,

00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:56.480
keep your mouth

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:57.600
shut.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:05:58.810
Understand?

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:09.120
You draw the big villa first.

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:10.850
Daddy is going to answer a call.

00:06:13.480 --> 00:06:16.880
Anjia Community, Building 4, Unit 4, Apartment 404.

00:06:18.480 --> 00:06:20.240
Firefly Dining Club.

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:24.280
Little London English Class.

00:06:26.640 --> 00:06:28.840
August Art Training School.

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:30.440
No...

00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:33.280
You...

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.040
Who are you?

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:37.720
What do you want?

00:06:37.960 --> 00:06:38.760
Tell me.

00:06:40.760 --> 00:06:42.000
You think with police protection,

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.520
you're safe?

00:06:44.159 --> 00:06:45.490
If you don't want to die,

00:06:47.520 --> 00:06:49.200
someone else will.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.659
Maybe it'll be your daughter.

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:54.640
She's alone way too often.

00:06:59.240 --> 00:07:01.100
Don't bring up my daughter, okay?

00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:03.120
I know who you are.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:04.720
Tell me.

00:07:05.320 --> 00:07:06.920
Tell me what you really want.

00:07:06.960 --> 00:07:08.480
I just want to see you.

00:07:09.320 --> 00:07:10.320
Which path to take

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:12.760
is up to you.

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.060
Every path leads to a dead end.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:19.640
When you chose this path,

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:23.340
you should have known there was no turning back.

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:25.940
There's no going back.

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:27.180
What are you doing?

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:28.440
Hello.

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.360
Officer.

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:00.360
Excuse me.

00:08:00.520 --> 00:08:02.120
Could you watch my daughter?

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:04.160
I need to go up and talk to the teacher.

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:04.760
Thank you.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:13.520
Caicai.

00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:16.930
Give Daddy a kiss, okay?

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:26.250
Daddy will definitely buy you a big house.

00:08:27.200 --> 00:08:27.680
Okay.

00:08:28.120 --> 00:08:29.050
I'm going up now.

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:44.770
Lin Xiao.

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:45.690
Captain Sun.

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:46.960
Liu Jiang ran away.

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:48.560
He said he was going to ask the kindergarten teacher something,

00:08:48.560 --> 00:08:49.760
asked us to watch the child,

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:52.420
and then jumped right off the second floor here.

00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:53.320
Chase him.

00:08:56.520 --> 00:08:57.280
Okay, got it.

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:58.200
Captain Sun.

00:08:58.200 --> 00:09:00.080
Someone saw Liu Jiang taking a taxi over there.

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:02.480
We've already contacted the taxi company.

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:04.800
Xiaohan, what do you think is going through his head?

00:09:04.800 --> 00:09:06.930
Doesn't he know we're protecting him?

00:09:07.800 --> 00:09:09.560
Wang Guifang only said the person was wearing a mask,

00:09:09.560 --> 00:09:11.620
so she couldn't see his face clearly.

00:09:11.720 --> 00:09:12.760
And she also said

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:13.960
Liu Jiang deserved to die.

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:15.760
Her only mistake was getting the wrong person.

00:09:15.760 --> 00:09:17.920
She still doesn't realize she was used.

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:18.960
Take her back to the station.

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:20.000
Calm her down.

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:21.920
Once she's emotionally stable,

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:23.050
find a sketch artist

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:24.360
to draw the killer's face.

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:25.090
Understood.

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:26.320
Master.

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:27.720
Master.

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:30.240
We've checked all the cameras in the urban village.

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:31.520
No camera captured that

00:09:31.520 --> 00:09:32.280
man in black.

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:35.740
Scouting the route in advance

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.980
and planning the escape path.

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:39.130
His usual style.

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:40.880
Can we determine

00:09:40.880 --> 00:09:42.210
which direction he ran?

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:45.960
Probably.

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:48.480
But there are still some confusing points.

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:50.940
Master, I think you need to see for yourself.

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:53.010
Let's go.

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:24.340
Such a short distance,

00:10:24.520 --> 00:10:25.560
stopping so many times,

00:10:25.560 --> 00:10:26.890
leaving so many traces.

00:10:27.400 --> 00:10:28.530
He did it on purpose.

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:30.120
He is provoking us.

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:32.160
Why?

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:33.360
Who is he?

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:46.880
Okay.

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:48.060
Coming right away.

00:10:48.760 --> 00:10:49.240
Master.

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:50.960
We found the taxi driver.

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:57.000
I drove him.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.880
We started from the urban village.

00:10:58.880 --> 00:11:00.080
He got off right here.

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:01.800
After he got off, he walked straight ahead.

00:11:01.800 --> 00:11:03.720
Then I turned around and went back to the city.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:04.840
He just walked away?

00:11:04.840 --> 00:11:06.240
He didn't get into another car?

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:06.970
I'm not sure.

00:11:07.160 --> 00:11:09.160
I didn't look back when I drove away.

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.760
According to the taxi driver,

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:18.090
this is the only road Liu Jiang could take.

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:20.020
But there is nothing on this road.

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:22.600
There's one more thing I don't understand.

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:24.320
What exactly was Liu Jiang afraid of?

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:25.440
Why did he run away?

00:11:25.760 --> 00:11:27.040
That bleeding doll

00:11:27.720 --> 00:11:29.320
was a threat from the killer.

00:11:29.800 --> 00:11:31.530
Liu Jiang also received a call.

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.000
I suspect it was the killer,

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:34.060
using his daughter

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:35.100
to threaten him

00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:37.320
and make him walk into a trap.

00:11:37.520 --> 00:11:38.720
If that's the case,

00:11:39.120 --> 00:11:41.560
the killer must know Liu Jiang very well.

00:11:42.840 --> 00:11:44.280
He has been observing Liu Jiang for a long time.

00:11:44.280 --> 00:11:45.960
The psychological motivation of serial killers

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:47.560
basically comes from power.

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:49.280
They seek the feeling of domination,

00:11:49.280 --> 00:11:50.140
manipulation,

00:11:50.160 --> 00:11:51.160
and control.

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:54.200
They only strike when they are absolutely certain.

00:11:54.200 --> 00:11:54.840
Liu Jiang

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:56.480
is probably doomed.

00:12:05.640 --> 00:12:07.770
There is a situation under the bridge.

00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:12.600
Go notify the fire department.

00:12:12.600 --> 00:12:13.880
Don't let the fire spread.

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:14.940
Already notified.

00:12:18.680 --> 00:12:19.520
What's the situation?

00:12:19.520 --> 00:12:20.920
It was like this when we got here.

00:12:20.920 --> 00:12:23.920
We're not sure yet if it's murder or self-immolation.

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:26.640
Hey.

00:12:29.680 --> 00:12:30.200
Captain Sun,

00:12:30.200 --> 00:12:30.680
look.

00:12:33.920 --> 00:12:34.520
Liu Jiang.

00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:36.720
No way.

00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:54.840
Sun Xun.

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:55.840
Secure the scene.

00:12:55.960 --> 00:12:56.690
Captain Sun.

00:13:55.800 --> 00:13:56.400
Sit tight.

00:14:49.240 --> 00:14:49.720
Right side.

00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:50.240
Get in.

00:15:22.120 --> 00:15:22.760
Up ahead.

00:15:30.040 --> 00:15:31.840
He's heading toward the relocation area again.

00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:32.900
He wants to go back.

00:15:33.040 --> 00:15:34.400
He left the relocation area,

00:15:34.400 --> 00:15:35.730
and now he's going back.

00:15:35.880 --> 00:15:37.200
His movements are too illogical.

00:15:37.200 --> 00:15:37.960
The more illogical it is,

00:15:37.960 --> 00:15:39.360
the more it highlights his purpose.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:39.840
Either

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:41.360
he's extremely familiar with that area

00:15:41.360 --> 00:15:43.280
and is completely confident he can escape from there,

00:15:43.280 --> 00:15:43.640
or

00:15:43.880 --> 00:15:45.000
he left a puzzle there

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:46.260
waiting for us to find.

00:16:48.640 --> 00:16:49.200
Ahead.

00:18:03.880 --> 00:18:04.560
Copy that.

00:18:06.680 --> 00:18:08.540
Still so many people at this hour.

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:10.200
There are no traffic lights in the relocation area.

00:18:10.200 --> 00:18:12.160
Many people take this route for a shortcut.

00:18:12.160 --> 00:18:13.240
I've called the traffic police and public security,

00:18:13.240 --> 00:18:14.720
and people from the nearby police station are coming over.

00:18:14.720 --> 00:18:16.400
They are searching along the streets.

00:18:16.400 --> 00:18:17.600
Everyone must register.

00:18:17.600 --> 00:18:19.680
Keep everyone who matches the description.

00:18:19.680 --> 00:18:20.810
Split up and search.

00:18:33.520 --> 00:18:34.520
Stop right there!

00:18:47.720 --> 00:18:48.560
Zhou Guannan!